data.description: This quintessential New England home is a classic. Extremely charming, welcoming and ready to entertain inside/out! The country kitchen, boasts a beautiful natural wood ceiling, a custom built-in cabinet, pendant lighting & a pantry.  Adjacent, is a large dining room, accompanied by high ceilings, built-in shelving and lovely hardwood floors, that expand through the living room and foyer. There is room for everyone in the spacious living room plus tons of natural lighting and high ceilings. The family room is definitely as bonus. This space is perfect to cozy up to the warm woodstove. You will find a bedroom and bathroom with a showerstall on the main level as well. Through the foyer, upstairs, there are 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. Opportunity knocks when completely finishing the walkup attic to instantly add value to the property. The expansive, flat and sunny back yard is absolutely awesome! Not to mention the shed with extra storage stalls. Great, desirable westside location!!
